N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 14 ยง 18.10 - Pending criminal process

State Regulations

Nothing in this Part shall affect: (a) the course of the pending criminal
process involving a prisoner being treated pursuant to this Part or, (b) any obligation of the warden or other
official to return the prisoner to court in the course of such criminal process
or, (c) any right of the prisoner
to be returned to court. Notes
